<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-76-0305 </DOCNO><TEXT>This book provides a working knowledge of a variety of analytical applicationsof x-ray diffraction and x-ray fluorescence. It presents the basic theoryof x-ray diffraction and fluorescence, a description of the instrumentation,and discussion of the usefulness and limitations of a number of x-rayand related techniques.</TEXT></DOC>